{"tid":2486849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[主祐女王] 1959年菲臘親王訪港記","createTime":"2021-04-13T06:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T14:40:53.000Z","uid":43150,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26158b9851ab81ec889b2bd89daada3caa72d56a","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"多謝we toast HK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主祐女王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖上頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wetoasthk.com/%e3%80%90%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e7%9a%87%e5%ae%a4%e3%80%911959%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%b2%e8%87%98%e8%a6%aa%e7%8e%8b%e8%a8%aa%e6%b8%af%e8%a8%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%258b%25b1%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%259a%2587%25e5%25ae%25a4%25e3%2580%25911959%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%258f%25b2%25e8%2587%2598%25e8%25a6%25aa%25e7%258e%258b%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%25a8%2598%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=0a20cd60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wetoasthk.com/%e3%80%90%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e7%9a%87%e5%ae%a4%e3%80%911959%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%b2%e8%87%98%e8%a6%aa%e7%8e%8b%e8%a8%aa%e6%b8%af%e8%a8%98/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/1959%E8%8F%B2%E8%87%98%E8%A6%AA%E7%8E%8B%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF.jpg?w=773&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F1959%25E8%258F%25B2%25E8%2587%2598%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF.jpg%3Fw%3D773%26ssl%3D1&h=918ed4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國王夫菲臘親王在二次大戰曾在皇家海軍服役，先後在地中海及法國南部作戰。在大戰最後階段，他在幼犬號（HMS Whelp）參與沖繩戰役和日本投降。 之後他便隨幼犬號來到香港，協助香港重光。據親王回憶，在日本駛往香港途中是他最高興的旅程之一，因為他們不用再關燈，也可以打開舷窗，甚至可以在海中暢泳。1959年，菲臘親王代表皇室進訪問香港。這次重臨舊地，他感慨香港戰後發展迅速，與他14年前來時已大大不同。現在我們跟菲臘親王遊覽一次50年代的香港吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Prince-Philip-Royal-Navy-officer-PA-cropped.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FPrince-Philip-Royal-Navy-officer-PA-cropped.jpg%3Fw%3D750%26ssl%3D1&h=a63dd0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二戰時期的菲臘親王。（圖片來源：AP)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Photo10ddWhelp3BrianRayner.jpg?w=765&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FPhoto10ddWhelp3BrianRayner.jpg%3Fw%3D765%26ssl%3D1&h=933ff347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1945年正前往來港的幼犬號HMS Whelp。(圖片來源：naval-history)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>皇后碼頭上岸，萬民景仰</strong><br />\n菲臘親王在3月6日下午一點幾到乘坐皇家遊艇不列顛尼亞號進入香港水域。負責迎接的駐港英軍軍艦添馬號、錫蘭號以及在尖沙咀訊號山的炮兵嗚炮二十一響向親王致敬。 當不列顛尼亞號在維港駛過時，海上的天星小輪、汽車渡輪、大大小小汽艇都響鞍致意。港督柏立基及其他政府官員、駐港英軍司令、行政、立法兩局議員以及大量市民早在碼頭等候。親王上岸後簡單檢閲在場英軍儀仗隊後便乘車前往港督府。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/1.jpg?resize=1024%2C763&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F1.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C763%26ssl%3D1&h=4c1b5c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港督柏立基在皇后碼頭歡迎親王。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/k20d3284.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fk20d3284.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=bc3f3d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大量香港市民在中環歡迎菲臘親王。(圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n不少市民在中環主要道路兩旁夾道歡迎親王，有人為睹親王風彩而瘋狂追車。<strong>有少女更表示親王漂亮英俊：「難怪女王都願嫁。」</strong> 港督府聚會、英京大酒樓晚宴 來港後首個行程便在港督府舉行party，親王在警察銀樂隊歡送下入場。Party會場衣香鬢影，菲臘親王與香港華人、洋人士紳有講有笑。新界六位非官守太平紳士李仲莊、鄧佩瓊等向親王獻上紀念冊，感謝英國皇室及女王陛下自香港開埠以來對於香港發展、自由、社會和諧的貢獻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/2.jpg?resize=1024%2C770&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F2.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C770%26ssl%3D1&h=db1060e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整個中環人山人海。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/6.jpg?resize=768%2C570&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F6.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C570%26ssl%3D1&h=5d977d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港督府聚會。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<br />\nParty過後菲臘親王馬不停蹄，先作無線電廣播，之後便到灣仔英京大酒家參與本地華人為他舉行之歡迎宴。席上有行政、立法兩局華人議員、名流仕紳，例如周竣年、周錫年、羅文錦、羅文惠、顏成坤、郭贊等等，為免有參加者失禮，大會一早提醒大家服裝要求：男裝若穿中服可穿長袍小掛、西服則穿燕尾服打上白/黑領結，純色西裝亦可接受；女裝則只可穿中服大掛或長旗袍。<br />\n<br />\n席上菜單也經過深思熟慮，配合西方口味之餘也保留廣東菜的特色：乳豬全體、雞絲大翅、碧玉珊瑚、清蒸大石班，揚州炒飯等，而親王最愛吃的竟然是咕嚕肉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/4.jpg?resize=768%2C571&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F4.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C571%26ssl%3D1&h=af9ac7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民在屋外掛上英國國旗。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/3.jpg?resize=1024%2C755&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F3.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C755%26ssl%3D1&h=948f17c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>三月七日</strong><br />\n啟德閱兵，為伊院奠基<br />\n三月七日是親王訪港的重頭戲，一大清早他便到啟德機場檢閲駐港英軍，在奏出國歌之後，三千名英軍包括海陸空三軍及香港防衛軍整齊列隊受檢。閲兵之後親王去到京士柏為伊利沙白醫院主持奠基典禮，<strong>並代表英女王向香港授予香港盾徽。</strong>同時親王為伊院將成為遠東最新型醫院，能夠加強保障香港人健康而高興。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/img151_0.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fimg151_0.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=3868c04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n菲臘親王大在啟德機場上岸。(圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/img114.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fimg114.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=b31c5328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n菲臘親王準備閱兵。（圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/img_3156-hug-1.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fimg_3156-hug-1.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=1092a649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n親王在吉普車上閱兵。（圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n<strong>四處參觀，重遇故人</strong><br />\n參觀醫院工地後，菲臘親王立即乘坐不列顛尼亞號招待香港青年工作者，<strong>而此時香港政府為親王找來了一位名為何桂英的水上婦人。原來在1945年香港重光時，何桂英父母曾為英軍艦艇刮擦油漆服務，當年親王與9歲的何桂英相識。</strong><br />\n<br />\n在前一天到港時，親王請香港警方代為尋找，警方出動20名警探並在舢板上廣播，最終為親王找到這名舊朋友。兩人透過翻譯談話，互相問候。<br />\n<br />\n之後親王又乘坐皇家空軍直升機從高空遊覽香港，又到工科專業學校參觀。"},{"pid":"09a3076cb6f0412b2bc5df6acd9ffc93f365139f","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:58:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>足球表演賽，文藝晚會</strong><br />\n為歡迎菲臘親王訪港，香港足總特意安排在嘉山球場舉行一場表演賽。對陣雙方為由職業華人球員組成的華聯及主要由英軍組成的西聯，雖然華聯有莫振華、姚卓然等星級球員，西聯球員仍希望在親王面前爭取表現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/%E5%B7%A5%E5%95%86%E6%99%9A%E5%A0%B1-1959-03-07-_%E7%88%B2%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E8%8F%B2%E8%87%98%E8%A6%AA%E7%8E%8B%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E8%92%9E%E5%A1%B2%E5%8F%83%E8%A7%80%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E7%9B%83%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E6%B1%BA%E8%B3%BD%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E5%A1%B2%E9%A4%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%8A%A0%E7%B2%89%E9%A3%BE%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B7%E6%87%B8%E9%97%98%E4%B8%B2%E7%87%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%95%AA-1.jpg?resize=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%2599%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1-1959-03-07-_%25E7%2588%25B2%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E8%258F%25B2%25E8%2587%2598%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2592%259E%25E5%25A1%25B2%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E7%259B%2583%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A1%25B2%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25B2%2589%25E9%25A3%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25B9%25B7%25E6%2587%25B8%25E9%2597%2598%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E7%2587%2588%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%258F%25A6%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2595%25AA-1.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C683%26ssl%3D1&h=e678d2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爲歡迎菲臘親王今日蒞塲參觀紀念盃足球決賽(工商晚報, 1959-03-07)<br />\n<br />\n球賽開始時親王仍未到達，而華聯亦顯示出職業球員能力，半場時已大炒對方5：1。半場休息時，親王千呼萬喚始出來，他向兩隊球員、教練問好，最後比賽以7：1結束。<br />\n<br />\n球賽過後，親王轉移到香港大球場參加由教育司署舉行的「青年表演大會」。表演項目有由女童軍表演的葡國土風舞、小童群益會及YMCA分別表演中國舞蹈、亦有舞龍、舞獅等充滿中國風彩表演。不過此日傳來羅文錦爵士因心臟病突發病逝的消息，昨日才相談甚歡，今日已陰陽相隔，令親王感到傷感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%A0%B1-1959-03-08_%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%9D%AF%E8%B3%BD%E5%A5%BD%E6%B3%A2%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%A0%B4%E6%B8%AF%E8%8F%AF%E4%B8%80%E9%BC%93%E4%BD%9C%E6%B0%A3%E8%A5%BF%E8%81%AF%E6%A3%84%E7%94%B2%E6%9B%B3%E5%85%B5%E4%B8%83%E5%80%8B%E7%9A%AE%E9%8C%A6%E6%A8%99%E8%90%BD%E6%B8%AF%E8%8F%AF.jpg?resize=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B1-1959-03-08_%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E6%259D%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BC%2593%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%2594%25B2%25E6%259B%25B3%25E5%2585%25B5%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%259A%25AE%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%258F%25AF.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C683%26ssl%3D1&h=0ec392e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紀念杯賽好波在上半場港華一鼓作氣西聯棄甲曳兵七個皮錦標落港華(大公報, 1959-03-08)<br />\n09)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>三月八日</strong><br />\n親王留港最後一天是星期日，他先到聖約翰教堂做禮拜，然後便在港島環島遊，途中發生一件小插曲。當親王坐駕來到薄扶林道時，三位香港大學何東Hall的女學生突然衝出馬路攔截坐駕，要向親王送上何東Hall小錦旗。親王沒有要女生「霜花杏仁露」（上返行人路），更友善道謝，盡顯親民一面。<br />\n<br />\n後來親王探訪香港仔，先後參觀魚市場及拜訪一户艇户，得到船主千金送花，令他笑得見牙不見眼。香港仔四處海上、岸上都掛有彩旗，更築有一大個牌樓，就像過年一樣熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n最後，親王在皇后碼頭登上不列顛尼亞號，駛離香港前往英屬所羅門群島訪問。當皇家遊艇在鯉魚門附近時，香港帆船會的帆船向親王發出歡送訊息。不列顛尼亞號也回覆：「感謝來訊，並請代為致意，祝佳運及順風。菲臘親王」<br />\n<br />\n1959年菲臘親王訪港之行是當年一大事件，而親王親民舉動，盡顯皇室的魅力及對香港厚愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/%E5%B7%A5%E5%95%86%E6%99%9A%E5%A0%B1-1959-03-09_%E6%94%94%E6%88%AA%E8%A6%AA%E7%8E%8B%E5%BA%A7%E9%A7%95%E8%BB%8A%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%BB%E9%8C%A6%E6%97%97-1.jpg?resize=1024%2C522&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%2599%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1-1959-03-09_%25E6%2594%2594%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E9%25A7%2595%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%258D%25BB%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%2597%2597-1.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C522%26ssl%3D1&h=eeddbfdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攔截親王座駕車港大女生獻錦旗(工商晚報, 1959-03-09)"},{"pid":"8a61e08af620fff583ee32ff516b1ac4c5be3d3e","tid":2486849,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e17cbb572fd940cddeac1b9f79adce2d4ed2de6","tid":2486849,"uid":210088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"高汁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995f642f3679b34195907e58c713b40a82131266","tid":2486849,"uid":152476,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_EHH4tlFj7I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_EHH4tlFj7I&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=58df5d06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_EHH4tlFj7I</a>"},{"pid":"ae6b6d9b07f77df99b9c94bd6c2254f78c6452a8","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"【菲臘親王嘅糖果】<br />\n<br />\n英國白金漢宮於香港時間傍晚，宣布菲臘親王逝世嘅消息，享年99歲。講起來，我同家中長輩都同佢有幾面之緣。<br />\n<br />\n細個嘅時候，我間中都有聽過長輩提起，以前喺添馬艦（即係佢哋所講嘅「舊鐸也」或Old Dockyard）同菲臘親王見過面兼傾過計。除咗喺1975年同1986年陪同英女皇訪港，菲臘親王早喺1959年，曾經官式訪問香港，當時佢仲要係坐住皇家遊艇Britannia飄洋過海咁嚟。不過一般報道較少提及嘅係，二次大戰期間，菲臘親王喺英國海軍服役，親自上戰場打仗；太平洋戰役後期，佢被任命為HMS Whelps少校，同其他盟軍喺東京灣接受日本投降，隨後戰艦去到香港，協助香港重光。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當時香港百廢待興，海軍基地殘破不堪，連原來嘅添馬艦都炸沉咗。長輩們（當時只係得幾歲至十零歲嘅姑婆同姨婆們）陸續返去Dockyard，幫嚟到香港嘅戰艦修繕同補給。包括呢位海軍少校在內嘅一班海軍，對佢哋非常友善，仲成日俾食物佢哋。嗰陣時，呢位年輕海軍軍官仲未同伊麗莎白公主訂婚，我家長輩當然唔會估到，佢後來成為親王。1959年，菲臘親王訪港嘅時候，仲特登去添馬艦探佢哋。當年仲有報紙報道，菲臘親王周圍問Dockyard嘅軍官：「當年喺戰艦甲板補油、我成日請食糖果嗰幾個細路女去咗邊？」</strong><br />\n<br />\n而小妹有幸同菲臘親王見面嘅機會，發生喺差不多十年前。當時Visit Britain安排嗰一個參觀白金漢宮嘅活動，邀請世界各地幾十人出席。記得幾十人被分成幾個小組，同我同組嘅有墨西哥、阿聯酋、南非同津巴布韋嘅代表；我哋「入宮」之前，工作人員再三叮囑，參觀嘅時候唔可以用手機、唔可以影相，到時會有活動攝影師，影咗嘅相會send返俾大家，但唔可以放上網或以任何形式公開。我哋過咗安檢之後，有一個直頭係《The Crown》入面管家咁嘅樣嘅人行出嚟，帶我哋行咗好幾個美侖美奐嘅大廳，詳細介紹每個廳房嘅歷史同故事。去到尾聲嘅時候，我哋被安排去咗另一個大廳，有茶同茶點招待。大家喺度嘆住皇家奶茶、傾傾吓交流緊嘅時候，突然全場靜晒，各人都識趣放低茶杯，乖乖咁企好，原來菲臘親王親自過嚟接見。<br />\n<br />\n菲臘親王走嚟同我哋逐一握手，問我哋嚟自邊度，然後閒聊幾句。<br />\n<strong>輪到我嗰陣，我話我嚟自香港。佢老人家即刻講：<br />\n「很好，我嚟過香港幾次。」<br />\n「多謝您嚟探訪。我嘅外婆同其他長輩，有同我講以前喺添馬艦見過您。」<br />\n「係呀，我打仗嘅時候已經去過。嗰陣時有啲好年輕嘅女工幫手工作。」</strong><br />\n（我知，你仲成日請佢哋食糖🥲）<br />\n<br />\n#RIP #PrincePhilip #GoodbyeHRH<br />\n#想當年 #英式糖果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/195770447859016/posts/945029369599783/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F195770447859016%2Fposts%2F945029369599783%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=572f0996\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/195770447859016/posts/945029369599783/</a>"},{"pid":"73db26ea149286d7e0760d805aaa5f7267f88fde","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e17cbb572fd940cddeac1b9f79adce2d4ed2de6","tid":2486849,"uid":210088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"高汁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1529ea967a53d03c9e97261582d8591e1e41fa","tid":2486849,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"高汁留名"},{"pid":"ef0e8fc38ce171a2f28374a4f6d2ce024231a66a","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2b8d80390a4b86f13a8eb7fe85731130217c67","tid":2486849,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦搶走香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509c9e62616b9aaeb693c332e204435fb2c1b621","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374bdbfc4b53f6e183e91e05d630cfba3b69d941","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef328752f4de52528c264a0fe8721a715f349424","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f45adda3f9721e3b95d7227980a64ab0a373722","tid":2486849,"uid":373900,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"26158b9851ab81ec889b2bd89daada3caa72d56a","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"多謝we toast HK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主祐女王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖上頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wetoasthk.com/%e3%80%90%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e7%9a%87%e5%ae%a4%e3%80%911959%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%b2%e8%87%98%e8%a6%aa%e7%8e%8b%e8%a8%aa%e6%b8%af%e8%a8%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%258b%25b1%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%259a%2587%25e5%25ae%25a4%25e3%2580%25911959%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%258f%25b2%25e8%2587%2598%25e8%25a6%25aa%25e7%258e%258b%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%25a8%2598%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=0a20cd60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wetoasthk.com/%e3%80%90%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e7%9a%87%e5%ae%a4%e3%80%911959%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%b2%e8%87%98%e8%a6%aa%e7%8e%8b%e8%a8%aa%e6%b8%af%e8%a8%98/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/1959%E8%8F%B2%E8%87%98%E8%A6%AA%E7%8E%8B%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF.jpg?w=773&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F1959%25E8%258F%25B2%25E8%2587%2598%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF.jpg%3Fw%3D773%26ssl%3D1&h=918ed4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國王夫菲臘親王在二次大戰曾在皇家海軍服役，先後在地中海及法國南部作戰。在大戰最後階段，他在幼犬號（HMS Whelp）參與沖繩戰役和日本投降。 之後他便隨幼犬號來到香港，協助香港重光。據親王回憶，在日本駛往香港途中是他最高興的旅程之一，因為他們不用再關燈，也可以打開舷窗，甚至可以在海中暢泳。1959年，菲臘親王代表皇室進訪問香港。這次重臨舊地，他感慨香港戰後發展迅速，與他14年前來時已大大不同。現在我們跟菲臘親王遊覽一次50年代的香港吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Prince-Philip-Royal-Navy-officer-PA-cropped.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FPrince-Philip-Royal-Navy-officer-PA-cropped.jpg%3Fw%3D750%26ssl%3D1&h=a63dd0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二戰時期的菲臘親王。（圖片來源：AP)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Photo10ddWhelp3BrianRayner.jpg?w=765&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FPhoto10ddWhelp3BrianRayner.jpg%3Fw%3D765%26ssl%3D1&h=933ff347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1945年正前往來港的幼犬號HMS Whelp。(圖片來源：naval-history)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>皇后碼頭上岸，萬民景仰</strong><br />\n菲臘親王在3月6日下午一點幾到乘坐皇家遊艇不列顛尼亞號進入香港水域。負責迎接的駐港英軍軍艦添馬號、錫蘭號以及在尖沙咀訊號山的炮兵嗚炮二十一響向親王致敬。 當不列顛尼亞號在維港駛過時，海上的天星小輪、汽車渡輪、大大小小汽艇都響鞍致意。港督柏立基及其他政府官員、駐港英軍司令、行政、立法兩局議員以及大量市民早在碼頭等候。親王上岸後簡單檢閲在場英軍儀仗隊後便乘車前往港督府。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/1.jpg?resize=1024%2C763&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F1.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C763%26ssl%3D1&h=4c1b5c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港督柏立基在皇后碼頭歡迎親王。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/k20d3284.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fk20d3284.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=bc3f3d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大量香港市民在中環歡迎菲臘親王。(圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n不少市民在中環主要道路兩旁夾道歡迎親王，有人為睹親王風彩而瘋狂追車。<strong>有少女更表示親王漂亮英俊：「難怪女王都願嫁。」</strong> 港督府聚會、英京大酒樓晚宴 來港後首個行程便在港督府舉行party，親王在警察銀樂隊歡送下入場。Party會場衣香鬢影，菲臘親王與香港華人、洋人士紳有講有笑。新界六位非官守太平紳士李仲莊、鄧佩瓊等向親王獻上紀念冊，感謝英國皇室及女王陛下自香港開埠以來對於香港發展、自由、社會和諧的貢獻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/2.jpg?resize=1024%2C770&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F2.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C770%26ssl%3D1&h=db1060e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整個中環人山人海。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/6.jpg?resize=768%2C570&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F6.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C570%26ssl%3D1&h=5d977d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港督府聚會。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<br />\nParty過後菲臘親王馬不停蹄，先作無線電廣播，之後便到灣仔英京大酒家參與本地華人為他舉行之歡迎宴。席上有行政、立法兩局華人議員、名流仕紳，例如周竣年、周錫年、羅文錦、羅文惠、顏成坤、郭贊等等，為免有參加者失禮，大會一早提醒大家服裝要求：男裝若穿中服可穿長袍小掛、西服則穿燕尾服打上白/黑領結，純色西裝亦可接受；女裝則只可穿中服大掛或長旗袍。<br />\n<br />\n席上菜單也經過深思熟慮，配合西方口味之餘也保留廣東菜的特色：乳豬全體、雞絲大翅、碧玉珊瑚、清蒸大石班，揚州炒飯等，而親王最愛吃的竟然是咕嚕肉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/4.jpg?resize=768%2C571&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F4.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C571%26ssl%3D1&h=af9ac7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民在屋外掛上英國國旗。（圖片來源：英國百代）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/3.jpg?resize=1024%2C755&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F3.jpg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C755%26ssl%3D1&h=948f17c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>三月七日</strong><br />\n啟德閱兵，為伊院奠基<br />\n三月七日是親王訪港的重頭戲，一大清早他便到啟德機場檢閲駐港英軍，在奏出國歌之後，三千名英軍包括海陸空三軍及香港防衛軍整齊列隊受檢。閲兵之後親王去到京士柏為伊利沙白醫院主持奠基典禮，<strong>並代表英女王向香港授予香港盾徽。</strong>同時親王為伊院將成為遠東最新型醫院，能夠加強保障香港人健康而高興。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/img151_0.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fimg151_0.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=3868c04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n菲臘親王大在啟德機場上岸。(圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/img114.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fimg114.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=b31c5328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n菲臘親王準備閱兵。（圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/img_3156-hug-1.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fimg_3156-hug-1.jpg%3Fw%3D640%26ssl%3D1&h=1092a649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n親王在吉普車上閱兵。（圖片來源：Gwulo)<br />\n<strong>四處參觀，重遇故人</strong><br />\n參觀醫院工地後，菲臘親王立即乘坐不列顛尼亞號招待香港青年工作者，<strong>而此時香港政府為親王找來了一位名為何桂英的水上婦人。原來在1945年香港重光時，何桂英父母曾為英軍艦艇刮擦油漆服務，當年親王與9歲的何桂英相識。</strong><br />\n<br />\n在前一天到港時，親王請香港警方代為尋找，警方出動20名警探並在舢板上廣播，最終為親王找到這名舊朋友。兩人透過翻譯談話，互相問候。<br />\n<br />\n之後親王又乘坐皇家空軍直升機從高空遊覽香港，又到工科專業學校參觀。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ojlFst4biiM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DojlFst4biiM&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=9086c160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ojlFst4biiM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HS1k8l3mdvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHS1k8l3mdvY&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=47358499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HS1k8l3mdvY</a><br />\nGod Save the Queen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d21db7594b18db9a3facc5519301590529862d5","tid":2486849,"uid":126977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"1ced4e232a1009d24242d73c84a013601afe9668","tid":2486849,"uid":6142,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:06:40.000Z","msg":"永遠唔可以忘記英國對我哋既恩"},{"pid":"ce0e6e0fa34e0dedd976b0165de01132a7c41177","tid":2486849,"uid":39503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e02e6a9044918518ebd9f93aa85f79c8248712b","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"聖上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「簡單來說，他一直是我力量的來源，長伴我走過這麼多年，我、他的整個家族還有英國與很多其他國家，都欠他非常多，遠超過他所說的。」<br />\n英女王伊利沙伯二世<br />\n<br />\n99歲辭世的 #菲臘親王 1934年在一場親戚的婚禮儀式上邂逅伊利沙伯公主，兩人相戀後，1947年11月20日在西敏寺舉行婚禮。伊利沙白當時還是公主，直至1952年才登基為女王。伊利沙白二世是英國歷史上在位時間最長君主，與菲臘親王的婚姻亦為英國所有君主中最長。<br />\n<br />\n1943年，菲臘趁聖誕到訪溫莎堡時，旁觀者已能看出兩人相戀的徵象，伊利沙伯把菲臘的照片放在壁爐架上，菲臘在二戰打仗期間也帶着伊利沙伯的照片。<br />\n<br />\n到了1946年，菲臘正式向當時約20歲的伊利沙伯求婚，歡天喜地的伊利沙伯當場答應，但事實上佐治六世有點擔心，他表示女兒太年輕，故此要求兩人先等一年時間，待伊利沙伯21歲時，才向外公布婚訊。<br />\n<br />\n菲臘在名義上是貴族，他與伊利沙伯同樣是維多利亞女王的後代，但與伊利沙伯的地位懸殊：菲臘出身自希臘王室、1921年在希臘出生，當地政局不穩，又與土耳其爆發戰爭，結果在菲臘還是手抱嬰兒的時候，希臘王室成員就遭流放，菲臘空有貴族名銜，實際是「窮親戚」，家庭不時要為財政問題憂心，希臘王室與英國王室差距是非常明顯。<br />\n<br />\n為迎娶伊利沙伯公主<br />\n#放棄希臘丹麥王室頭銜<br />\n兩人結婚是開心事，但對於菲臘親王來說，他也有不少犧牲，他捨棄希臘王室與丹麥王室的名銜，正式入籍英國，他原本沒有姓氏，於是使用母親的家族姓氏蒙巴頓（Mountbatten），以英國平民身份迎娶伊利沙伯，但對他來說更大的犧牲，應該是離開海軍工作，變成全職的王室成員。<br />\n<br />\n1947年11月20日，兩人在倫敦西敏寺（Westminster Abbey）大婚。<br />\n<br />\n在位60多年，菲臘親王向英女王獻計無數，帶來不少正面影響，早在1956年，他就成功說服英女王打破平民貴族的隔閡，邀請各界人士作非官式的聚會，不論藝人、記者，還是工程師及企業家均會獲女王召見，同時女王亦藉着這些聚會接觸社會上不同階層人士，好讓女王能體察民情，不斷革新王室制度，以適應新時代。<br />\n<br />\n他還提議開放王宮予公眾參觀，又在溫莎堡等王室領地設立商店，售賣領地耕種出來的農產品。不曾停下來的開放步伐，在菲臘親王的建議下只會快不會慢，連女王的私人畫廊都開放予公眾欣賞。<strong>另外，菲臘親王又設立連香港人也受惠的愛丁堡公爵獎勵計劃（本港愛丁堡獎勵計劃97年後改稱為香港青年獎勵計劃）培育年輕人，再次將王室與民眾的距離拉近。</strong><br />\n<br />\n踏入21世紀，菲臘親王因年事已高，身體健康逐漸變差。2008、2012年菲臘親王因病住院，在2017年決定退休，卸下所有公職。2019年1月，97歳的菲臘親王在駕車時遇上交通意外，兩日後再度駕駛時，被拍到未有佩帶安全帶。菲臘親王決定在3星期後，自願放棄駕駛執照。<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbEo6x8Lz4rbw47eXNMHfkdadweuDuMfQzUMkjxhsQrjK?filename=U4As9tw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4As9tw.jpg&h=62ecfa5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPTN5QEQ1hYcGHqCTpeF8V5B9c1dZ35DhnhJzmjDBFXBm?filename=V2QQnOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2QQnOw.jpg&h=9b2c188c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSr6w6zQ6ghWCgvSpLD8jFirxmmL5ukQLk8MuwbXE7RMi?filename=289xA8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F289xA8w.jpg&h=cd19237d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP5fjjg5but5kQk7KKU4X2oUgouPX8P5JNg37aXecATco?filename=Q3sSA8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3sSA8w.jpg&h=a585612e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPqt3wnSWeoLnnPcZjs5nLbBBX2YNvFbEaGaXjZiMvdFv?filename=F9b0K1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9b0K1R.jpg&h=c8398aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直至今年2月16日，英國王室指菲臘親王遵從醫囑而入院，屬「預防措施」，及後一直未有出院，並須接受心臟手術，終於周五早上（4月9日）於溫莎堡安詳離世。<br />\n<br />\n#GSTQ<br />\n#GSTD<br />\n<br />\nSource: media / HK01<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3907377369308077&amp;id=183874271658424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3907377369308077%26id%3D183874271658424&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=311068af\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3907377369308077&amp;id=183874271658424</a>"},{"pid":"d55d4ccc124ea4a9844e4d230451014a9a7f414a","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7b57927b434dc3729fe8b4fc269d52bb9a0b6d","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7b58e9c5c060323eb17f6cfe0f63421b84660614","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:50:45.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6e2eaa43456cbbac57c60e540329de03292d8e","tid":2486849,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"好好睇"},{"pid":"940bcb4486eb7aac3ad566bba26896a414ae262a","tid":2486849,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed6e2eaa43456cbbac57c60e540329de03292d8e","tid":2486849,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"好好睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-